<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not clinging on to anything.</font>

290
00:12:27,850 --> 00:12:30,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you still care so much 
about Miyako-san,</font>

291
00:12:30,780 --> 00:12:34,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">why not just come back to Strawberry 
Productions instead of sneaking around?</font>

292
00:12:34,980 --> 00:12:36,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've got unfinished business.</font>

293
00:12:37,530 --> 00:12:40,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't drag her into it.</font>

294
00:12:40,200 --> 00:12:41,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Unfinished business"?</font>

295
00:12:42,530 --> 00:12:44,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You of all people should know.</font>

296
00:12:45,630 --> 00:12:49,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I need to murder the bastard 
who did that to Ai.</font>

297
00:12:50,040 --> 00:12:53,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you were just her agent.</font>

298
00:12:53,610 --> 00:12:55,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why go that far?</font>

299
00:12:58,130 --> 00:12:59,300
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="16"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#998b92">Ai's Fan for All Eternity!!!</font></font></font></b></font>

300
00:13:16,100 --> 00:13:20,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ai may have been your mother,</font>

301
00:13:20,300 --> 00:13:24,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but she was also like a daughter to me.</font>

302
00:13:24,590 --> 00:13:25,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh...</font>

303
00:13:27,950 --> 00:13:29,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I get it.</font>

304
00:13:29,470 --> 00:13:32,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's why I went into showbiz, too.</font>

305
00:13:34,380 --> 00:13:37,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The mastermind was someone close to Ai.</font>

306
00:13:38,470 --> 00:13:42,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I thought joining her business 
would get me closer to the truth.</font>

307
00:13:43,320 --> 00:13:45,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But here's the answer I found.</font>

308
00:13:47,260 --> 00:13:50,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The man who killed Ai is dead.</font>

309
00:13:56,580 --> 00:14:00,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I met someone who I shared 
paternal DNA with.</font>

310
00:13:57,110 --> 00:13:58,110
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font color="#17180e"><font size="24">Private DNA Test Report

<font size="18">Result: It was determined that there
is a high possibility the individuals
are half-siblings who share the
same biological father.</font></font></font></b></font>

311
00:14:00,690 --> 00:14:02,360
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="12"><font color="#595765">Bodies of Married Couple Found
In Apparent Double Suicide</font></font></b></font>

312
00:14:00,690 --> 00:14:04,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our dad was Seijuurou Uehara, 
and he's already gone.</font>

313
00:14:04,670 --> 00:14:08,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So our quest for revenge is over.</font>

314
00:14:09,260 --> 00:14:11,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's no need to keep doing—</font>

315
00:14:14,610 --> 00:14:15,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kid...</font>

316
00:14:16,200 --> 00:14:17,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you talking about?</font>

317
00:14:18,160 --> 00:14:20,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I remember that incident well.</font>

318
00:14:21,120 --> 00:14:23,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Plus when it happened, 
and how I found out.</font>

319
00:14:23,760 --> 00:14:25,640
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="8"><font color="#8c8080">Signs Point to Double Suicide</font></font></b></font>

320
00:14:23,760 --> 00:14:25,640
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Arial Black"><font color="#fcfdfb"><font size="13">Breaking:  <font color="#d62b31">Actors Airi Himekawa and Seijuurou Uehara <font color="#8c8080">Found Dead in Villa</font></font></font></font></font></b></font>

321
00:14:24,180 --> 00:14:27,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}It was when I was having a prep meeting 
with Ai for the Tokyo Dome concert.</font>

322
00:14:25,640 --> 00:14:26,140
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="12"><font color="#776b6c">Signs point to double suicide</font></font></b></font>

323
00:14:25,640 --> 00:14:26,140
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Arial Black"><font color="#fcfdfb"><font size="28">Breaking:  <font color="#b80009">Actors Airi Himekawa and Seijuurou Uehara <font color="#594d4a">Found Dead in Villa</font></font></font></font></font></b></font>

324
00:14:26,140 --> 00:14:27,850
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="12"><font color="#b1a49f">Seijuurou Uehara, Actor</font></font></b></font>

325
00:14:26,140 --> 00:14:27,850
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="12"><font color="#b1a49f">Airi Himekawa, Actor</font></font></b></font>

326
00:14:28,140 --> 00:14:32,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seijuurou Uehara masterminded 
Ai's murder? That's impossible.</font>

327
00:14:32,780 --> 00:14:35,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He died before you guys moved.</font>

328
00:14:35,680 --> 00:14:38,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How could a dead guy 
have known your new address?</font>

329
00:14:38,730 --> 00:14:41,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The timeline makes no sense.</font>

330
00:14:41,370 --> 00:14:43,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But the DNA test...</font>

331
00:14:43,250 --> 00:14:45,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you consider the possibility 
of paternity fraud?</font>

332
00:14:46,490 --> 00:14:50,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The mother could've had the kid with 
a man other than her husband, you know?</font>

333
00:14:50,990 --> 00:14:53,500
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="18"><font color="#493c39"><font face="Arial Black">Bodies of Married Couple Found In Apparent Double Suicide

<font size="16"><font face="Arial">A man and a woman were found unresponsive
in a cottage in Karuizawa. They were taken to
a hospital where they were declared dead.
A statement from the Nagano Prefectural Police
identified the deceased as actor Airi Himekawa
and fellow actor Seijuurou Uehara.</font></font></font></font></font></b></font>

334
00:14:51,320 --> 00:14:54,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Uehara deaths 
could've been a murder-suicide</font>

335
00:14:54,640 --> 00:14:58,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">caused by an enraged husband who'd just 
found out about his wife's adultery, no?</font>

336
00:14:59,130 --> 00:15:02,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Before all that, why are you so convinced 
that your dad was the mastermind?</font>

337
00:15:02,630 --> 00:15:06,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Someone at the agency 
could've leaked the address, too.</font>

338
00:15:06,510 --> 00:15:09,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This isn't over. Not even close.</font>

339
00:15:10,270 --> 00:15:13,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've always been a smart kid.</font>

340
00:15:13,380 --> 00:15:17,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you'd thought about it for one second, 
you would've realized this yourself.</font>

341
00:15:17,260 --> 00:15:18,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And yet...</font>

342
00:15:18,230 --> 00:15:20,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've got it wrong, Ichigo-san.</font>

343
00:15:21,580 --> 00:15:24,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're overlooking something crucial.</font>

344
00:15:25,140 --> 00:15:26,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Something crucial? What's that?</font>

345
00:15:26,700 --> 00:15:28,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You have to be!</font>

346
00:15:29,110 --> 00:15:31,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's gotta be something!</font>

347
00:15:35,500 --> 00:15:39,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It can't be... This can't be right.</font>

348
00:15:40,110 --> 00:15:42,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was sure it was all over, finally...</font>

349
00:15:43,950 --> 00:15:45,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's over, right?</font>

350
00:15:45,220 --> 00:15:46,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean...</font>

351
00:15:46,310 --> 00:15:50,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My bad. That was all just guesswork.</font>

352
00:15:50,900 --> 00:15:54,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You go home and get some rest.</font>

353
00:16:06,320 --> 00:16:09,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've decided to start dating 
Akane for real.</font>

354
00:16:16,170 --> 00:16:17,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry, let me off here.</font>

355
00:16:26,010 --> 00:16:30,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No... there's no way. It was all over.</font>

356
00:16:30,860 --> 00:16:33,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ai's already been avenged.</font>

357
00:16:33,770 --> 00:16:35,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If not, then I...</font>

358
00:16:35,560 --> 00:16:38,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isn't that great? We have our goal back!</font>

359
00:16:39,710 --> 00:16:42,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We can be driven by hatred alone,</font>

360
00:16:42,720 --> 00:16:45,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">find the guy who killed Ai for real,</font>

361
00:16:46,430 --> 00:16:50,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and put him through all the suffering 
this world has to offer.</font>

362
00:16:50,450 --> 00:16:51,160
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="17"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#413d38">Ai's Fan for All Eternity!!!</font></font></font></b></font>

363
00:16:51,430 --> 00:16:53,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I deserve to suffer.</font>

364
00:16:54,270 --> 00:16:58,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have no right to enjoy my life 
after I let Ai die before my very eyes.</font>

365
00:16:59,190 --> 00:17:01,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is punishment. Retribution.</font>

366
00:17:01,960 --> 00:17:06,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No! I finally got the chance 
to live my life!</font>

367
00:17:06,300 --> 00:17:10,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The peace you've had lately 
was just a passing dream.</font>

368
00:17:10,100 --> 00:17:11,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Forget about it.</font>

369
00:17:11,620 --> 00:17:15,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After all, we haven't put 
an end to anything at all.</font>

370
00:17:15,010 --> 00:17:16,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take revenge.</font>

371
00:17:16,480 --> 00:17:17,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get payback.</font>

372
00:17:18,150 --> 00:17:21,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Think of what Ai went through. Punish him.</font>

373
00:17:18,930 --> 00:17:19,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Aqua...</font>

374
00:17:20,600 --> 00:17:21,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Aqua?</font>

375
00:17:22,060 --> 00:17:24,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For what we lost forever!</font>

376
00:17:23,100 --> 00:17:23,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Aqua!</font>

377
00:17:25,190 --> 00:17:26,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aqua!</font>

378
00:17:26,190 --> 00:17:27,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shut up!</font>

379
00:17:41,020 --> 00:17:42,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did I...</font>

380
00:17:42,500 --> 00:17:45,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did I do something to make you 
hate me so much?</font>

381
00:17:47,860 --> 00:17:51,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so stupid. I didn't have a clue.</font>

382
00:17:52,290 --> 00:17:53,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so sorry, Aqua.</font>

383
00:18:21,470 --> 00:18:23,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Hello? Aqua-kun?</i></font>

384
00:18:23,440 --> 00:18:25,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is now a good time?</font>

385
00:18:25,930 --> 00:18:30,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, you've got the Japan Film Awards 
ceremony tomorrow, huh?</font>

386
00:18:30,590 --> 00:18:34,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, though I'm only one of the several 
rookie actor award recipients.</font>

387
00:18:34,870 --> 00:18:38,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Still, it's a red-carpet event! 
I'm getting nervous!</font>

388
00:18:38,180 --> 00:18:41,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Even you still get nervous sometimes, huh?</i></font>

389
00:18:41,400 --> 00:18:42,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course I do.</font>

390
00:18:44,630 --> 00:18:45,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So...</font>

391
00:18:46,300 --> 00:18:49,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can we meet up tomorrow night?</font>

392
00:18:50,410 --> 00:18:52,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It'll have to be quite late 
because there's a wrap party,</i></font>

393
00:18:52,800 --> 00:18:54,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but I want you to see the dress 
I'll be wearing—</i></font>

394
00:18:54,500 --> 00:18:55,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry.</font>

395
00:18:56,570 --> 00:18:59,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I kinda don't feel like 
seeing anyone right now.</font>

396
00:19:01,030 --> 00:19:04,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really? Okay, I understand.</font>

397
00:19:04,980 --> 00:19:08,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If it ever gets too much, 
I'm always here for you, okay?</font>

398
00:19:08,030 --> 00:19:09,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Thanks, Akane.</i></font>

399
00:19:09,980 --> 00:19:11,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure. Bye.</font>

400
00:19:12,460 --> 00:19:13,090
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="12"><font color="#a49695">Aqua-kun</font></font></b></font>

401
00:19:12,940 --> 00:19:15,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Aqua-kun had been in 
good spirits lately, too.</i></font>

402
00:19:13,090 --> 00:19:15,090
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="12"><font color="#756966">Aqua-kun</font></font></b></font>

403
00:19:13,090 --> 00:19:15,090
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="8"><font color="#756966">Call ended</font></font></b></font>

404
00:19:16,230 --> 00:19:20,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>According to Ruby-chan, 
he wasn't always this gloomy guy.</i></font>

405
00:19:21,110 --> 00:19:24,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I bet things changed after Ai-san's death.</i></font>

406
00:19:25,080 --> 00:19:29,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Aqua-kun has panic attacks 
whenever he remembers her.</i></font>

407
00:19:29,480 --> 00:19:31,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>His childhood scars 
always remain with him,</i></font>

408
00:19:32,280 --> 00:19:33,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>almost like a curse.</i></font>

409
00:19:34,710 --> 00:19:40,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Now that he's free from avenging his 
mother, his guilt is fading gradually,</i></font>

410
00:19:35,860 --> 00:19:37,820
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Arial Black"><font color="#c69fe7">Hey, that's mine!</font></font></b></font>

411
00:19:36,360 --> 00:19:38,070
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Arial Black"><font color="#f5a591">aah</font></font></b></font>

412
00:19:37,950 --> 00:19:40,280
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Arial Black"><font color="#f691b4">pout</font></font></b></font>

413
00:19:38,320 --> 00:19:40,280
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Arial Black"><font color="#b6c6f9">Just kidding.</font></font></b></font>

414
00:19:40,900 --> 00:19:43,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and he's becoming the person 
he was always meant to be.</i></font>

415
00:19:44,760 --> 00:19:46,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can't help but hope...</i></font>

416
00:19:46,940 --> 00:19:51,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>that he remains oblivious 
and lives a peaceful life.</i></font>

417
00:19:51,910 --> 00:19:53,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Then I'm sure Aqua-kun will...</i></font>

418
00:19:54,990 --> 00:19:58,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">With the acting chops 
cultivated by her years in theater,</font>

419
00:19:57,380 --> 00:19:58,500
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="20"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#edddd4">Rookie Actor Award</font></font></font></b></font>

420
00:19:58,830 --> 00:20:01,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kurokawa-san has shone brightly 
in a variety of roles and productions.</font>

421
00:20:02,310 --> 00:20:05,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Congratulations on winning 
the Rookie Actor Award.</font>

422
00:20:08,140 --> 00:20:10,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so happy for you.</font>

423
00:20:10,610 --> 00:20:12,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're crying more than me.</font>

424
00:20:14,110 --> 00:20:15,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Aqua-kun?</i></font>

425
00:20:15,950 --> 00:20:17,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Nah, there's no way.</i></font>

426
00:20:19,240 --> 00:20:20,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow!</font>

427
00:20:20,760 --> 00:20:23,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The flower stand from the agency is huge!</font>

428
00:20:23,210 --> 00:20:24,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If not now, then when?</font>

429
00:20:25,250 --> 00:20:28,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow... the one from Lalalai is tiny.</font>

430
00:20:28,770 --> 00:20:31,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Times are tough for us 
theater groups, okay?</font>

431
00:20:31,790 --> 00:20:33,460
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="16"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#cd3c48">Celebrating the Rookie Actor Award
<font color="#655955">Theater Group Lalalai</font></font></font></font></b></font>

432
00:20:31,790 --> 00:20:33,620
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="16"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#cd3c48">Celebrating the Rookie Actor Award
<font color="#655955">Akane Kurokawa-sama</font></font></font></font></b></font>

433
00:20:32,690 --> 00:20:35,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">White roses? Who are these from?</font>

434
00:20:35,820 --> 00:20:37,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A former member of Lalalai.</font>

435
00:20:37,780 --> 00:20:42,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He runs his own agency now 
and sends flowers any time we're involved.</font>

436
00:20:42,980 --> 00:20:45,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All kinds of people are 
congratulating me, huh?</font>

437
00:20:45,990 --> 00:20:48,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Never forget to stay grateful.</font>

438
00:20:48,820 --> 00:20:50,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course!</font>

439
00:20:50,350 --> 00:20:55,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Man, who'd've thought Akane would 
make such a rapid rise to stardom?</font>

440
00:20:55,070 --> 00:20:57,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's all thanks to 
Kindaichi-san's coaching.</font>

441
00:20:57,940 --> 00:20:59,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please.</font>

442
00:20:59,100 --> 00:21:03,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's always had the skills, 
but in this business,</font>

443
00:21:03,260 --> 00:21:06,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you need to make a positive impression 
on the people with casting powers,</font>

444
00:21:06,190 --> 00:21:08,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">or it's hard to land lead roles.</font>

445
00:21:08,920 --> 00:21:13,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">President, your decision to put her 
on TV no matter what is paying off now.</font>

446
00:21:13,860 --> 00:21:16,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It seemed like an awful call at first,</font>

447
00:21:16,440 --> 00:21:20,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but ever since <i>Love for Real</i>, 
her public persona did a 180.</font>

448
00:21:21,280 --> 00:21:23,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is it, the look in her eyes?</font>

449
00:21:23,210 --> 00:21:25,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's usually so gentle,</font>

450
00:21:25,950 --> 00:21:29,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but when the cameras are on her, 
