453
00:21:38,920 --> 00:21:41,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For an actor, they're the ultimate gift.</font>

454
00:21:44,980 --> 00:21:46,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We had one of those in the past, too.</font>

455
00:21:46,900 --> 00:21:48,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really? Who was it?</font>

456
00:21:48,890 --> 00:21:51,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The one who sent those roses back there.</font>

457
00:21:51,220 --> 00:21:53,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He was one of our best actors.</font>

458
00:21:53,910 --> 00:21:55,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd love to watch him!</font>

